Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:51.83,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(950,950)\pos(392,478)\fsp5\blur2}被封锁的砂 水虎的反击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到木葉的援軍是你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為男人不能總是欠女人的情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.96,0:00:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是一樣 滿嘴男人女人的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.63,0:00:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅和勘九郎 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追那個挾持村裡女孩的傢伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡沒問題 你們趕快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據已知的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經分別開戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.05,0:00:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影子到不了她那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的二人組正趕往支援
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安排得很周到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然麻煩 但要做就做到最好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次不允許犧牲 力求完美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你這次不要在我面前哭鼻子了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:01:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都過去那麼久了 還記得這麼清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人就是如此麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.18,0:01:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼好像有點多餘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就把你們一起解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.29,0:01:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然向木葉求援啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂隱竟然如此墮落了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:02:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗只要受人恩惠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定會想著報恩的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是我的赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗的報恩 挺嚇人的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外兩個也會有人去援助的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就認真應對這場戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口氣不小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個廢物想聯手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你們不是龍眼伸縮劍的對手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要查克拉無法凝聚 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的砂就起不了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些砂只能迷迷對手的眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:04:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺到了 你的查克拉正被我吸收著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 葫蘆裡居然還有砂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經很小心了 沒想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是砂瀑我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪被稱為終極武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終極武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他無法超越工匠村所打造的忍具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他壓根就佔據絕對優勢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能還上人情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強的風 怎麼會有這麼強的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.49,0:06:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 應該是那兩把劍增幅了她的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她攻守都依賴那兩把劍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只能把她拉到忍術的範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能應對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正有點悶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙一直在努力保持和手鞠的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的注意力集中在遠處的手鞠身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這些中近距離型施術者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦靠近就用風將我們吹走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獸人分身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部分倍化之術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手臂 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙通牙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是過來搗亂的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是暗示你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本毫無默契嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在開玩笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打就好好打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在這兒叫囂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便鎧甲有減傷的功效…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是守鶴的宿主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂隱的終極武器 我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你已經落入我們的圈套了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 對手在我的施術範圍之外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且附近也沒有能延長影子的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼鬼祟祟地想幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問那麼多 待會兒再解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就告訴我能不能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們看看 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:09:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們製造的忍具有多厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股查克拉是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…水脈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了 三個點構成的三角形
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是結界 而是水脈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍具結界.逆鱗陣 啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆鱗陣的目標最初就鎖定了我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的劍用查克拉刺中水脈 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召喚出水龍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂子吸取大量的水後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會變得和鉛一樣重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我愛羅就無法操控砂子了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.55,0:11:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別慌 小李和鳴人已經趕過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一定會幫我愛羅脫困的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們集中精力對付眼前的對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然選擇摔在了砂地上 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是砂瀑我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用再掙扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉旋風
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄總是在最關鍵的時刻出現
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了 我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次奪回佐助時 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們曾來幫助過我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我們還人情來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你趕快去救你的學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你竟然被傷成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小李 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫他療傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去幫鳴人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先讓我和他較量一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點 他的鎧甲會吸收查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把你們的查克拉都吸光的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就無法使出平時的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有查克拉 也能靠氣勢取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 再加上強大的毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不出我所料 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間沒有任何攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明援兵沒有遠距離的施術者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就保持這個距離
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用風撕裂你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁敵方只注意到鹿丸他們 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心亂身…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我沒注意到你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想靠近我 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的把戲我早看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井野 你先待著別動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們了 志乃 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀑布處有傷者一名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通牙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.49,0:15:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部分倍化之術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…故意戲弄我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我吸乾了你們的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再好好教訓你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞傷已經治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他消耗的查克拉太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自同伴的消息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井野受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…你的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事了 去救你的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉強自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:16:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嗎 快去救你的同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但首先速度解決掉這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濃眉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 亂來是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的狗呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著黑螞蟻的零件 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次牙通牙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.44,0:16:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用烏鴉掩護我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丁次 你也要掩護我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真會使喚人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要開始反擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 你的術根本傷不到我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試才知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:16:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風遁.大鐮鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打哪兒呢 壓根沒目標嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 我明明看穿你的攻擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你見識一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是透明的水 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼粗也會產生影子的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我利用瀑布的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓施術範圍延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影子模仿術 成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通靈之術.斬斬舞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解決掉一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費了好大的勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然幫不上任何忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都這麼努力 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井野
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經無砂可用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是… 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂之鎧甲解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂子吸收了水分 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且被吸光了查克拉 應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快去 接下來交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獸人分身.牙通牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部分倍化之術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像蒼蠅一樣煩死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍眼神縮劍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傀儡演劇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.79,0:19:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑秘技.機機一發
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個背著小孩的忍者…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.49,0:20:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正朝山谷方向前進…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅正在追 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要緊吧 濃眉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻等會兒就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.84,0:20:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去追我愛羅了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我隨後就趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查出四天像人的真實身份了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是痛恨忍者五大國的 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工匠村的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們完成了禁忌的研究 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.40,0:22:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算製造終極武器
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.58,0:22:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.78,0:22:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他居民心生恐懼 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以避難去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.74,0:22:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.66,0:22:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你即刻趕往事發地點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.68,0:22:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甦醒的終極武器
